Claude Code Investigation:
--------------------------

  Critical Issue: dk.tbsalling:aismessages

  This dependency (used in ais-io for NMEA parsing) is licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 3.0, which prohibits commercial use.
  If this project is used commercially, you need to either:
  1. Contact the author (Thomas Borg Salling) for a commercial license
  2. Replace it with a commercially-licensed AIS parser

  All Other Dependencies: Clean

